data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! This is it! If you're looking for a home with 2.41 acres of privacy with no restrictions and no HOA, then this is it! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home has all the features you are looking for in a home. The second you walk through the front door you are greeted with the inviting open floor plan overlooking the living room into the kitchen. The kitchen offers unlimited counter and cabinet space with stainless steel appliances and a breakfast area off to the side. Off the living room and down the hall you have 2 spacious bedrooms and a full bath. The main bedroom is located off the kitchen with a spacious walk in closet, double vanity sink in the bathroom with a large walk in shower. The fenced in backyard gives you all the space for endless opportunities. You even have a separate 20x20 carport outback. Great location with close proximity Ballantyne, Fort Mill and Charlotte, you have everything you need at the tip of your fingers.
